Class Storage

  • java.lang.Object
    • Storage

  • public class Storage
extends java.lang.Object
    This class stores Item objects that can be manipulated by Command objects. it utilizes a hashmap based on the output of the has() function from each Item object.
    Since:
    5/08/18
